The following protocols are used for communication over the air interface (the radio link between the UE and the
eNodeB
). This protocol suite is is generally divided into three layers:
Radio Resource Control (RRC)
operating at layer 3;
Packet Data Convergence Protocol (PDCP)
operating at layer 2;
Radio Link Control (RLC)
operating at layer 2;
Medium Access Control (MAC)
operating at layer 2;
Physical Access (PHY)
operating at layer 1.
LTE Network Protocols
